{"tid":1841174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲醫護同狗有咩分別？","createTime":"2020-01-25T07:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:12.000Z","uid":196544,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69041688967d0ecf98428196431f2a7535c38dfc","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:30:00.000Z","msg":"狗話自己職責所在<br />\n打鳩香港人<br />\n醫護話自己職責所在<br />\n要救人<br />\n屌你老母偽善到<br />\n<br />\n你都係得果幾個原因姐<br />\n第一驚比人清算<br />\n我屌你老母臭閪<br />\n個班自私醫護狗驚比人清算？<br />\n幾多人因為場運動比人清算？<br />\n到呢個會救到709萬人既時候<br />\n你地縮埋返入病房？<br />\n<br />\n第二想救人<br />\n香港人有700萬人唔救<br />\n去救個政府<br />\n你地係冇腦定有自殺傾向<br />\n你屋企人點算？<br />\n肺炎既道德高地值幾多仔人命？<br />\n係想救人建議行上武漢做嘢<br />\n<br />\n第三職責所在<br />\n學生有冇話自己職責所在唔出嚟？<br />\n狗又話自己職責所以要打鳩我地<br />\n你地同狗既分別只係<br />\n一個有OT又比較安全<br />\n一個冇OT 仲可能冇左條命<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到自己咁偉大<br />\n你地有出糧架嘛<br />\n份人工令你接受到不公義事情<br />\n你咪唔好罷囉<br />\n你淆底姐<br />\n<br />\n講嘢係咁難聽<br />\n係想救人唔該你救呢700萬人<br />\n你話唔救肺炎撚（屌你都冇藥架啦）<br />\n直到封關<br />\n希望唔係所有醫護都好似果個感歎號既死左膠"},{"pid":"e7cba496588cbadbcde76bd2ffffff2b9cb02c3b","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0811a7d84cefb1e4c037f5c102e83c46c854a4","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f29335ed135d3b6cb06eaf523fb6c510734d015","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468f6180fff4548c78f32824db04135b3c5c5aff","tid":1841174,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"罷工啦屌<br />\n醫藍屍就係殺港<br />\n講撚完<br />\n-0-0"},{"pid":"afa8da7519ecfed543839c50c1fc9e2000ad8662","tid":1841174,"uid":321854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"你話我仆街都係咁講 一句講曬都係個錢字 供緊樓?條命重要定錢重要?"},{"pid":"a627fdf4f38a78f7b3c7d0eef4923c525553bdda","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fa35dda88d3d0e13723645a75ab3bd15800300","tid":1841174,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa8da7519ecfed543839c50c1fc9e2000ad8662","tid":1841174,"uid":321854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"你話我仆街都係咁講 一句講曬都係個錢字 供緊樓?條命重要定錢重要?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"佢地眼中供樓&gt;一切"},{"pid":"3030d1f28faeeb81984590864c38b80221448797","tid":1841174,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95fa35dda88d3d0e13723645a75ab3bd15800300","tid":1841174,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afa8da7519ecfed543839c50c1fc9e2000ad8662","tid":1841174,"uid":321854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"你話我仆街都係咁講 一句講曬都係個錢字 供緊樓?條命重要定錢重要?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"佢地眼中供樓&gt;一切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:12.000Z","msg":"仲要好偉大咁講救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}